1. Project Full Name

文具(wenju) - Writing Tools


2. Project Purpose and Summarization

文具将包括一系列中文编写工具,如输入法等。其中的TIM (Table-based Input Method)
是GTK+ 2的一个键盘输入模块,该输入法由其转换码表控制,你可以方便地修改码表来定
义自己的输入法。含有一完整的五笔码表作为例子。拟逐渐增加更多的码表及其他工具。
A collection of writing tools (wenju in Chinese pinyin) such as input method,
text file formatter, etc.  All the tools are based on Unicode.

It is not easy to find suitable writing tools for Chinese.  Over the years,
I have to build up my own collection, and I intend to add more to it.  Those
tools are developed on Linux using primarily C.  By starting the 'wenju'
project, I hope I can better organize the tools and other people may find
them useful too. 


3. License

GPL


4. Project Public Description

A collection of writing tools (wenju in Chinese pinyin) such as input method,
text file formatter, etc.  All the tools are based on Unicode.


